Cucumber Notes

BDD: Behavior Driven Development
GWT framework

given: pre-conditions
when: steps to perform
then: exp op

Scenario: Validate Send Friend Request feature
Given user is on login page
When user enters username and password
ANd user clicks on login button
And user enters some text in search friend field
And user selects one person
And user clicks on Send Friend Request
Then request should be sent to that user

Scenario Outline:
Run same scenario with multiple set of data
Examples keyword to give the input data
